high_descs: Turn to your left and go to the outer most, back corner of the bath tub.
Grab the pump bottle on the corner of the bath tub.
Move over to your right so that you are in front of the green, garbage bin.
Put the pump bottle inside the green garbage bin.
anns.task_desc: Put the pump bottle in the trash.

high_descs: Go left to the trash can next to the tub.
Pick up the soap bottle on the tub to the left.
Move to the trash can with the soap.
Put the soap in the trash can.
anns.task_desc: Put a soap bottle in the trash can.

high_descs: move to the bin  to the left of the sink
pick up a dispenser from the tub edge
move to the bin to the left of the sink
put a dispenser in the bin
anns.task_desc: Put a dispenser in the bin.
